3448
02:34:02.985 --> 02:34:04.145
or financial advisors.

3449
02:34:05.425 --> 02:34:07.125
We use AI and open banking

3450
02:34:07.305 --> 02:34:09.205
to streamline the mortgage application process.

3451
02:34:10.245 --> 02:34:12.325
Customers can complete a full credit application

3452
02:34:12.465 --> 02:34:15.245
and apply to multiple lenders under 10 minutes.

3453
02:34:16.305 --> 02:34:18.545
This is the first platform of its kind in New Zealand.

3454
02:34:19.405 --> 02:34:22.625
At its core, homely is about giving customers more

3455
02:34:22.625 --> 02:34:25.465
transparency, more choice, more control,

3456
02:34:25.885 --> 02:34:27.745
so they can compare competing offers

3457
02:34:27.885 --> 02:34:29.825
and select the best options for their needs.

3458
02:34:30.685 --> 02:34:32.585
Homely aims to create a level playing field

3459
02:34:32.655 --> 02:34:35.025
between large banks and smaller lenders.

3460
02:34:35.895 --> 02:34:38.785
Lenders compete based on pricing product features

3461
02:34:38.805 --> 02:34:41.585
and service without any advisor driven bias.

3462
02:34:42.535 --> 02:34:45.625
